<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Contrat Freelance - {{employee.firstName}} {{employee.lastName}}</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }

  .header {
    background: #1a1a2e;
    color: white;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .company-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .doc-title { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.7; text-align: right; }
  .doc-ref { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }

  .body { padding: 40px; }
  .section { margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #ec489a;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #ec489a; padding-bottom: 6px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .field { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .field-label { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .field-value { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a2e; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }

  .intro-text {
    background: #fdf2f8; border-left: 4px solid #ec489a;
    padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    margin-bottom: 24px; font-style: italic; color: #444;
  }

  .article { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .article-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #1a1a2e; }
  .article-body { color: #444; font-size: 12px; }

  .signature-section {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px;
    margin-top: 50px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  }
  .signature-box { text-align: center; }
  .signature-label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .signature-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 50px; }
  .signature-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a2e; margin: 0 20px; }
  .signature-caption { font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-top: 4px; }

  .footer {
    background: #f5f5f5; padding: 16px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold;
    background: #fce7f3; color: #9d174d;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div>
    <div class="company-name">{{company.name}}</div>
    <div style="font-size:11px; opacity:0.6; margin-top:4px;">Le Client</div>
  </div>
  <div class="doc-title">
    <div>CONTRAT DE PRESTATION DE SERVICE</div>
    <div class="doc-ref">#{{contract.id}}</div>
    <div style="font-size:11px; opacity:0.7; margin-top:4px;">Prestation du {{formatDate contract.startDate}}</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="body">
  <div class="intro-text">
    Entre <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> (ci-après "le Client") 
    et <strong>{{employee.firstName}} {{employee.lastName}}</strong> (ci-après "le Prestataire"),
    il a été convenu le présent contrat de prestation de services.
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Informations</div>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Client</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{company.name}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Prestataire</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{employee.firstName}} {{employee.lastName}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Service</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{position.title}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Informations prestation</div>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Type</div>
        <div class="field-value"><span class="badge">FREELANCE</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Date début</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{formatDate contract.startDate}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Date fin</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{#if contract.endDate}}{{formatDate contract.endDate}}{{else}}Indéterminée{{/if}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <div class="field-label">Honoraires</div>
        <div class="field-value">{{formatMoney contract.baseSalary}} / mois</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">Clauses de la prestation</div>

    <div class="article">
      <div class="article-title">Article 1 – Objet</div>
      <div class="article-body">
        Le Prestataire fournira des prestations de <strong>{{position.title}}</strong>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article">
      <div class="article-title">Article 2 – Durée</div>
      <div class="article-body">
        Prestation à compter du <strong>{{formatDate contract.startDate}}</strong>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article">
      <div class="article-title">Article 3 – Honoraires</div>
      <div class="article-body">
        Honoraires mensuels de <strong>{{formatMoney contract.baseSalary}}</strong> sur facture.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article">
      <div class="article-title">Article 4 – Indépendance</div>
      <div class="article-body">
        Le Prestataire agit en indépendant, sans lien de subordination.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="article">
      <div class="article-title">Article 5 – Facturation</div>
      <div class="article-body">
        Facture mensuelle à adresser au Client. Règlement à 30 jours.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-section">
    <div class="signature-box">
      <div class="signature-label">Le Client</div>
      <div class="signature-name">{{company.name}}</div>
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-box">
      <div class="signature-label">Le Prestataire</div>
      <div class="signature-name">{{employee.firstName}} {{employee.lastName}}</div>
      <div class="signature-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <span>{{company.name}}</span>
  <span>Freelance #{{contract.id}} — {{today}}</span>
</div>

</body>
</html>